# Installation
* Go to your krita folder: `{KRITA}\pykrita`
  * In windows: `%APPDATA%\krita\pykrita`
* Copy files from this repo (Except README)
* In Krita settings, activate new plugin `Easy Animate`

# ⚠️ Be aware
* Unfortunately Krita is not capable of running scripts correctly.
* Scripts that people write - often workarounds.
* This script is not exception. it may crash, and it's not recommended to use (without `Ctrl+S` habbit)
* Rather take this script as an __example__ to __develop__ yours. Just put somewhere my name if so
